/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f9d7ee48cc7c1aaab75034c361f43e454226c8","tid":408414,"uid":146496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T09:41:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9e133ade53cfcbe34efee381084d0046cc02b7d","tid":408414,"uid":18230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"雪濃湯，度度都有。<br />\n廣藏市場綠豆餅豬肉餅，唔好食血腸。<br />\n明洞香苑，食粥，試過好好食，台灣日本客多。<br />\n王妃家，烤肉定食，都抵食。<br />\n元堂脊骨土豆湯，食薯仔排骨湯，3個人食中size一鍋已經好飽。<br />\n全州中央會館，普通韓國野食，石頭窩飯，冷麵，煎餅，炒粉絲⋯⋯味道我覺得ok。"},{"pid":"02358f4b219016d02cb0fec3b2f011831cea0a0a","tid":408414,"uid":57549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T09:59:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完返黎<br />\n有當地人帶我食唔同野<br />\n去果度當地人排曬隊果啲<br />\n只能講一句，佢地平時食開屎"},{"pid":"61e90af6f9cfd580ddbb8ffd632ea59dfb9af737","tid":408414,"uid":50647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"你Download個app 叫mango plate<br />\n佢地嘅Openrice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0173a90324d1393188aefca809c28c8ce99c3325","tid":408414,"uid":18230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:04:06.000Z","msg":"之前食過豆漿麵，我自己覺得幾好食，不過我喺汝矣島嗰邊食，你過開去就試下，叫晉州會館。其他地方⋯⋯聽過景福宮嗰邊有。希望依家仲有得食，入秋後開始冇。"},{"pid":"1e8f8c29d63e07fee32e2bb9f9ed9b3e371d4ac5","tid":408414,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:24:15.000Z","msg":"陳玉華老奶奶一隻雞<br />\n南大門豬手<br />\n馬場食韓牛"},{"pid":"73062d7956aecd05dbe6b654b452c0cf2651f195","tid":408414,"uid":60982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"明洞街邊野又貴又唔好食<br />\n<br />\n馬場洞食韓牛<br />\n行下市場食豬腳 豬皮 綠豆餅<br />\n炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493987454704237afd9c9aee6a4c64445d393140","tid":408414,"uid":16712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><